Frogooo.PackageHelpThree: To copy the tracking number, first you need to go to “me” then go to “shipped” after that press button of “track order” on your overseas shopping platform.
Frogooo.PackageHelpFour: Under shipping info or logistic info, you can find the tracking number of the package and please copy and submit it to frogooo website.
